201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not attend the military expeditions and fight in jihad alongside you?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo, rather the best and most beautiful jihad for you is the Hajj, a blessed pilgrimage.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1861\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3076,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/28\/salat-description-adhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":39882,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Description of call to prayer, its wording","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mahdhurah reported: The Prophet of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught the call to prayer like this, \u201cAllah is the greatest. Allah is greatest. I bear witness there is no God but Allah. I bear witness there is no God but Allah. I bear witness Muhammad is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36569,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/03\/jihad-no-war-combat-killing\/","url_meta":{"origin":39882,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Jihad for women without fighting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is jihad a duty upon women?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes, jihad is a duty upon them in w